Technical notes

Pulp workers reduced to 2 (from default 6) due to 16GB RAM constraint ‚Äî OOM kills observed during initial content sync with default worker count. Tune upward if RAM is increased to 32GB.

DNS zone used: caal.dev ‚Äî AD DNS replication for calix.local zone was unreliable during build. PTR record created in caal.dev zone to match Satellite server naming convention.

Capsule firewall: only port 443/https open. Port 9090 handled internally by satellite-installer. No additional ports required on capsule host-based firewall.



